1
00:00:34,220 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:38,000
Your Highness.

3
00:00:38,719 --> 00:00:42,960
It's said that a child's blood
mixes with their parents'.

4
00:00:43,479 --> 00:00:45,399
To make them give up,

5
00:00:45,759 --> 00:00:48,039
one drop of blood is enough.

6
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:49,159
Insolent peasants!

7
00:00:49,479 --> 00:00:51,240
I'm a Lady titled by His Majesty.

8
00:00:51,479 --> 00:00:53,000
You can't just take my blood!

9
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:56,200
Please have mercy on us, My Lady.

10
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:57,560
Grant us a drop of blood.

11
00:01:00,359 --> 00:01:02,719
Wenyue, you knew this would happen.

12
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:04,400
Why did you bring me here?

13
00:01:04,879 --> 00:01:06,519
As a Princess Consort,

14
00:01:06,840 --> 00:01:08,439
I must care for the people.

15
00:01:08,879 --> 00:01:11,560
And I won't gamble the manor's honor.

16
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:15,319
Ms. Meng spoke for the people.

17
00:01:16,079 --> 00:01:17,680
Just bear with it for a moment.

18
00:01:19,280 --> 00:01:20,239
Your Highness.

19
00:01:21,239 --> 00:01:24,319
I happen to have a silver needle here.

20
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:25,200
No need.

21
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:27,640
Mine will be cleaner.

22
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:28,480
My Lady, no!

23
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:29,879
If you do this,

24
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:31,519
your family will lose face.

25
00:01:33,159 --> 00:01:34,640
Your Highness, no!

26
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:37,159
Lady Cheng'en is being threatened,

27
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:37,719
but...

28
00:01:37,719 --> 00:01:38,439
Luoxia.

29
00:01:39,319 --> 00:01:40,760
Take her blood.

30
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:41,760
Yes.

31
00:01:42,239 --> 00:01:45,480
My Lady can't give blood in public.

32
00:01:46,319 --> 00:01:47,640
If you hadn't reminded me,

33
00:01:48,040 --> 00:01:50,040
I'd have lost my temper
with these peasants.

34
00:01:51,120 --> 00:01:53,079
Wenyue, please spare
my family's face.

35
00:01:53,519 --> 00:01:55,079
I can't give blood in public.

36
00:01:56,079 --> 00:01:56,799
Granted.

37
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:58,000
Luoxia.

38
00:01:58,480 --> 00:01:59,840
Accompany her to take the blood.

39
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:00,920
Yes.

40
00:02:17,380 --> 00:02:21,220
=Episode 7=

41
00:02:21,759 --> 00:02:22,560
Mr. Liu.

42
00:02:23,759 --> 00:02:24,800
News from the gang.

43
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:27,159
Miss Rulan's parents were silenced
and taken to the suburbs.

44
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,479
Oh no!

45
00:02:35,879 --> 00:02:37,840
Your Highness, the blood is taken.

46
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:38,919
Nanny Du.

47
00:03:02,039 --> 00:03:03,240
Your Highness, look.

48
00:03:03,360 --> 00:03:04,520
The blood mixed.

49
00:03:06,080 --> 00:03:07,319
The blood mixed.

50
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:10,360
So you're sure they're my parents?

51
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:11,479
Of course.

52
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,879
No mistake at all?

53
00:03:12,919 --> 00:03:14,080
No mistake at all.

54
00:03:14,240 --> 00:03:15,520
You're not Ruoheng.

55
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,919
Who are you really?

56
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:18,919
You dared to impersonate a Lady!

57
00:03:19,759 --> 00:03:22,800
How dare you attack in front of me!

58
00:03:23,159 --> 00:03:25,319
Impersonating a Lady is a capital crime!

59
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,919
Wenyue, don't rush to judgment.

60
00:03:27,879 --> 00:03:29,159
Xiaojiu, come out.

61
00:03:32,439 --> 00:03:36,400
What if I say this is rabbit blood?

62
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:38,680
Luoxia.

63
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:40,240
Whose blood did you take just now?

64
00:03:40,479 --> 00:03:42,319
Your Highness, it was rabbit blood.

65
00:03:43,560 --> 00:03:44,439
Forgive me, Your Highness.

66
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:46,159
I told Luoxia not to speak.

67
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:48,360
I only wanted to clear
Lady Cheng'en's name.

68
00:03:48,719 --> 00:03:50,039
If you must punish someone,

69
00:03:50,479 --> 00:03:51,319
punish me.

70
00:03:51,520 --> 00:03:53,400
Enough, stand up.

71
00:03:54,599 --> 00:03:55,400
Wu Lian.

72
00:03:55,520 --> 00:03:56,719
Control your people.

73
00:03:56,879 --> 00:03:58,759
I won't tolerate this nonsense anymore.

74
00:04:02,759 --> 00:04:03,599
Nanny Du.

75
00:04:22,680 --> 00:04:25,560
It mixed? How is that possible?

76
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:28,639
I received news

77
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:29,560
that tomorrow's outing

78
00:04:29,560 --> 00:04:30,439
may cause trouble.

79
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:31,680
Prepare in advance.

80
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:36,879
Xiaojiu, hunt an animal for me tomorrow.

81
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:40,040
Xiaotao, follow me and act accordingly.

82
00:04:40,120 --> 00:04:40,839
Yes.

83
00:04:40,879 --> 00:04:41,600
Meng Wan.

84
00:04:41,839 --> 00:04:42,839
Do you know your crime?

85
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,240
Meng Wan.

86
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,399
Your misplaced kindness

87
00:04:47,879 --> 00:04:49,240
was used by schemers.

88
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,439
Do you know your crime?

89
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:55,279
Even if
Lady Cheng'en looks like your daughter,

90
00:04:55,319 --> 00:04:56,920
you shouldn't falsely accuse her!

91
00:04:57,240 --> 00:04:58,560
You dared to slander Lady Cheng'en!

92
00:04:58,639 --> 00:04:59,720
Your intentions are evil!

93
00:05:00,959 --> 00:05:01,959
Forgive me, Your Highness!

94
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,160
Your Highness.

95
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:04,959
About today's incident...

96
00:05:04,959 --> 00:05:05,680
Wu Lian.

97
00:05:06,079 --> 00:05:07,720
I trust you deeply,

98
00:05:07,920 --> 00:05:09,759
but your people made a mistake today.

99
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,920
Ruoheng has been wronged.

100
00:05:12,319 --> 00:05:13,879
I'm handing you over to Ruoheng.

101
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,639
You'll take whatever punishment
she gives.

102
00:05:15,879 --> 00:05:17,439
Until she forgives you.

103
00:05:18,680 --> 00:05:19,560
Yes, Your Highness.

104
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,399
This has ruined my mood.

105
00:05:21,879 --> 00:05:22,680
Return to the manor.

106
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:34,839
Lady Cheng'en,

107
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:38,319
please forgive us.

108
00:05:44,519 --> 00:05:46,839
Master Wu, you've been favored
by the Princess Consort for years.

109
00:05:47,439 --> 00:05:50,920
Did you ever think
you'd end up in my hands?

110
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,639
What exactly do you want?

111
00:05:53,519 --> 00:05:55,040
I learned how to punish people

112
00:05:55,319 --> 00:05:56,959
from you, Master Wu.

113
00:05:57,519 --> 00:05:59,920
Guess which trick I'll use.

114
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:07,040
(You reap what you sow.)

115
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,720
(It's too late now.)

116
00:06:09,680 --> 00:06:10,879
(Let fate decide our fates.)

117
00:06:11,360 --> 00:06:14,319
Make Master Wu walk
behind the carriage.

118
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:24,519
Useless trash.

119
00:06:26,040 --> 00:06:27,920
Better off dead.

120
00:06:30,319 --> 00:06:31,240
Clean up the mess.

121
00:06:31,920 --> 00:06:32,519
Understood.

122
00:06:33,079 --> 00:06:35,600
Master Wu, stop dragging your feet.

123
00:06:35,639 --> 00:06:36,519
Hurry up and follow.

124
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:38,600
Sniveling lapdog.

125
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:42,279
I obey your orders, Lady Cheng'en.

126
00:06:42,439 --> 00:06:43,519
Behave yourself.

127
00:07:01,700 --> 00:07:05,860
(Jingyuan Manor)

128
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,800
Is Ruoheng back?

129
00:07:11,560 --> 00:07:12,360
Yes.

130
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:16,360
But she locked her courtyard
immediately upon returning.

131
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:18,959
Smoke is billowing from inside.

132
00:07:19,759 --> 00:07:20,759
No one knows why.

133
00:07:22,319 --> 00:07:24,399
She suffered a huge humiliation today.

134
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:26,759
She's taking it out on Wu Lian.

135
00:07:27,680 --> 00:07:29,040
Let her be.

136
00:07:29,839 --> 00:07:30,759
But Your Highness,

137
00:07:31,040 --> 00:07:34,399
don't you find the blood test today

138
00:07:34,759 --> 00:07:35,920
suspicious?

139
00:07:36,079 --> 00:07:37,959
As long as it doesn't interfere
with our plans,

140
00:07:38,079 --> 00:07:39,120
it's fine.

141
00:07:39,879 --> 00:07:41,600
We'll deal with everything

142
00:07:41,879 --> 00:07:43,920
after the Flower Festival,

143
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:46,519
when the Prince returns to the capital.

144
00:07:47,759 --> 00:07:48,839
Ruoheng or Wu Lian,

145
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:49,920
they're all tools we need.

146
00:07:50,279 --> 00:07:51,959
As long as they're useful,

147
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:54,240
why bother worrying

148
00:07:56,639 --> 00:07:58,000
about their childish squabbles?

149
00:07:58,000 --> 00:08:00,519
It's just like kids fighting.

150
00:08:01,519 --> 00:08:02,839
Yes, Your Highness.

151
00:08:03,879 --> 00:08:04,680
Luoxia.

152
00:08:05,120 --> 00:08:06,120
Go check on them.

153
00:08:06,639 --> 00:08:08,639
As long as they don't cause a scene,

154
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:10,759
no need to report back.

155
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:11,680
Yes.

156
00:08:16,439 --> 00:08:18,959
Master, it's been hours.

157
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:20,600
No sign of her at all.

158
00:08:21,480 --> 00:08:24,040
Let me help you up first.

159
00:08:25,639 --> 00:08:27,399
No matter what she does,

160
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,839
as long as she's in this manor,

161
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:32,360
she's under my control.

162
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:55,639
We're told to back them up now.

163
00:08:55,639 --> 00:08:57,360
They don't trust that woman.

164
00:09:05,240 --> 00:09:06,000
Eat up, little ones.

165
00:09:06,399 --> 00:09:08,519
Master didn't forget you.

166
00:09:24,559 --> 00:09:26,440
I hope Mr. Liu succeeds

167
00:09:26,759 --> 00:09:28,240
and finds that list.

168
00:09:29,720 --> 00:09:31,879
My Lady, it's getting dark.

169
00:09:31,879 --> 00:09:33,480
Wu Lian is still kneeling outside,

170
00:09:33,679 --> 00:09:35,200
waiting for your punishment.

171
00:09:38,679 --> 00:09:40,000
He's clever.

172
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:40,879
What do you mean?

173
00:09:42,440 --> 00:09:43,559
Kneeling here lets

174
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:45,360
the Princess Consort's people see

175
00:09:45,679 --> 00:09:47,320
he's accepted his punishment.

176
00:09:47,879 --> 00:09:49,080
If I don't forgive him,

177
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:51,279
I'll seem ungenerous.

178
00:09:51,759 --> 00:09:52,720
Then what should we do?

179
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:02,600
He's miscalculated.

180
00:10:03,759 --> 00:10:07,159
Master, let me tell
the Princess Consort you fainted.

181
00:10:07,399 --> 00:10:08,559
That way, you can avoid this.

182
00:10:08,639 --> 00:10:11,200
Do you think hiding now

183
00:10:13,519 --> 00:10:15,399
will make that woman

184
00:10:16,279 --> 00:10:18,200
spare me?

185
00:10:23,639 --> 00:10:24,440
Lady Cheng'en,

186
00:10:24,879 --> 00:10:28,639
please forgive me
for doubting your identity.

187
00:10:29,080 --> 00:10:30,440
Please punish me.

188
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:33,200
Even if you take my life,

189
00:10:33,840 --> 00:10:35,159
I have no complaints.

190
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,240
How convenient.

191
00:10:38,519 --> 00:10:41,960
I don't want your worthless life.

192
00:10:43,440 --> 00:10:44,559
But your hands...

193
00:10:50,559 --> 00:10:51,519
Master Wu.

194
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:55,000
I heard your hands are
legendary in Jinxiu City.

195
00:10:55,440 --> 00:10:58,519
They used to hold needles and thread.

196
00:10:59,559 --> 00:11:00,440
Today,

197
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:04,919
I'll make needles
and thread pierce them.

198
00:11:05,279 --> 00:11:06,080
No!

199
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:40,340
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

200
00:11:40,580 --> 00:11:43,580
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

201
00:11:44,780 --> 00:11:47,540
♪The past no longer binds♪

202
00:11:48,020 --> 00:11:51,740
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

203
00:11:52,180 --> 00:11:56,300
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

204
00:11:57,140 --> 00:12:00,020
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

205
00:12:00,380 --> 00:12:02,380
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

206
00:12:02,380 --> 00:12:06,460
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

207
00:12:06,860 --> 00:12:09,060
♪For your faith that never broke♪

208
00:12:09,260 --> 00:12:13,380
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

209
00:12:14,260 --> 00:12:16,180
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

210
00:12:16,180 --> 00:12:20,420
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

211
00:12:21,620 --> 00:12:24,100
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

212
00:12:24,220 --> 00:12:26,860
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

213
00:12:26,860 --> 00:12:29,460
♪One thought turns into ash♪

214
00:12:30,420 --> 00:12:35,780
♪No future left to write♪

215
00:12:36,860 --> 00:12:38,660
♪If I never fall♪

216
00:12:38,700 --> 00:12:41,060
♪How could this waiting end♪

217
00:12:41,060 --> 00:12:42,420
♪If I bear no scars♪

218
00:12:42,420 --> 00:12:44,740
♪How could I challenge fate♪

219
00:12:44,740 --> 00:12:47,100
♪I knew there was no way back♪

220
00:12:47,100 --> 00:12:51,100
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

221
00:12:51,220 --> 00:12:53,340
♪For your faith that never broke♪

222
00:12:53,540 --> 00:12:57,500
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

223
00:12:58,460 --> 00:13:00,380
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

224
00:13:00,380 --> 00:13:04,780
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

225
00:13:05,860 --> 00:13:08,460
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

226
00:13:08,500 --> 00:13:11,060
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

227
00:13:11,060 --> 00:13:13,420
♪One thought turns into ash♪

228
00:13:14,540 --> 00:13:19,780
♪No future left to write♪

229
00:13:20,660 --> 00:13:23,060
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

230
00:13:24,340 --> 00:13:26,460
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

231
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:30,340
♪If we meet again someday♪

232
00:13:30,780 --> 00:13:36,580
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
